checkOut

T checkOut()
Requests an object to work on from the sink. The sink should mark the object as "being processed" and not return it again until either reportSuccess or reportFailure were called. Returns null if there is currently nothing that could be checked out. A sink may choose to block a requesting thread until something becomes available.
